---
title: Creamy Cauliflower & Bacon Penne with Pear & Cucumber Salad
description: Mac ’n’ cheese is the ultimate family side dish – but it needs a little help to transform it into a satisfying meal. So, we’ve added bacon and golden roasted cauliflower to take this classic to the next level, plus a green salad to contrast the rich sauce.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-cauliflower-bacon-penne-7b05ce20.jpg
